This project is a fork of loading_indicator (https://github.com/TinoGuo/loading_indicator),
originally created by TinoGuo and licensed under the Apache License 2.0.

The original package provides a collection of loading animations written in pure Dart
for Flutter applications, inspired by loaders.css and NVActivityIndicatorView. It includes
34 different animation types ranging from simple pulse animations to complex geometric patterns.

This fork aims to:
1. Modernize the codebase for current Flutter/Dart SDK versions
2. Update outdated dependencies
3. Add comprehensive test coverage
4. Maintain active development and support

The original work remains copyrighted by its respective owners and continues to be
licensed under the Apache License 2.0.
